  "problemSolved": {
    "statement": "Cognee is an open-source knowledge engine that lets you ingest data in any format or structure and continuously learns to provide the right context for AI agents. It combines vector search, graph databases and cognitive science approaches to make your documents both searchable by meaning and connected by relationships as they change and evolve.",
    "cynefinDomain": "complex"
